This is the Simple Dynamic Programming problem.&lt;br&gt;
Consider this as the 2D array *Arr[4][4]*
```
[{ 0, 0, 0, 6 }, 
  { 2, 0, 0, 2 }, 
  { 0, 1, 1, 1 }, 
