First thing you need is to initialise the base cases.&lt;br&gt; 
So first column and last row is our base case.&lt;br&gt;
```dp[0][3]=Arr[0][3];```&lt;br&gt;

After this for first column&lt;br&gt;
```dp[i][0]=dp[i+1][0]+Arr[i][0];```&lt;br&gt;

For last row&lt;br&gt;
```dp[3][i]=dp[3][i-1]+Arr[3][i];```&lt;br&gt;

For other values&lt;br&gt;
